Build articles

Usage: mf build [OPTIONS] <ARTICLE>

Arguments:
  <ARTICLE>  

Options:
      --config <PATH>      
      --project <PROJECT>  
      --output <OUTPUT>    
  -v, --verbose...         
      --dry-run            
  -q, --quiet              
      --format <FORMAT>    [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --no-color           
  -h, --help               Print help
  -V, --version            Print version
